"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/PpDWjKoKgbzhevgJFh_nv.jpeg?height=1080&width=1080)\\n\\nCanadian talent Avry has been expanding his sound through a string of singles—covering r&b, indie pop and dance—and now he's back with our favorite from him yet, \\\"Petals.\\\"⁣\\n⁣\\nOn the track, soothing guitar licks and nostalgic drums form the perfect base for Avry to showcase his clean-cut vocals. Between infectious melodies and his gentle delivery, Avry has us hooked, leaving us feeling like we've been transported back to blissful summer days.⁣\\n⁣\\nWe’re certain there’s a lot more to come from Avry, so be sure to get on board early.⁣\\n\\n[https://youtu.be/PeFFWIi7qOc](https://youtu.be/PeFFWIi7qOc)\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/beforethedata/status/1455262421166137344](https://twitter.com/beforethedata/status/1455262421166137344)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1635796589,\"title\":\"Vancouver-based Avry releases a soothing, summertime anthem with “Petals”\",\"publication\":\"beforethedata\"},\"digest\":\"gTjsxoSjL9iUjGSy8-zE9qJmqnhcF9P-cp1YBOMwNMU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xdFBB06683a882E827907422dbFE836E5430fE2aC\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"atsR1tMj1SsOo02HGSMv2SfByxb-Twy9T-NGp_j5J9k\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"v9z9nTbjUOquAr-PNe0DMuB8W-xEguCp4oXLfPb-puA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"hoFDCP6Q_maaUmVI63DD6eENa0QDjch_K21XGQPeijH4wEj4J-Jp5hBU_oDq_0RTHGeBw1sHtjkdAvs7RGsKeQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xd53dceb764d68329f5d336cf5bf8dd7cf1330f61b53c780d21cdcdc68235e72f68cffbfd1a62f895bcef20619e7387fbbd35eedb878bc48bd620724450f878de1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"atsR1tMj1SsOo02HGSMv2SfByxb-Twy9T-NGp_j5J9k\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"v9z9nTbjUOquAr-PNe0DMuB8W-xEguCp4oXLfPb-puA\\\"}\"